question: How many panel descriptions are there?
query: select count(distinct erc_panels.description) from project_erc_panels join erc_panels on project_erc_panels.panel = erc_panels.code

question: Find titles of projects which started earlier than 2016
query: SELECT title FROM projects WHERE start_year < 2016

question: Show titles of programmes which have FP7 as parent program
query: select title from programmes where parent = 'FP7'

question: What are all of the ways that projects members can participate in projects?
query: SELECT pmr.description from project_member_roles as pmr

question: Get names of project members who's activity type description is Research Organisations
query: select member_name from project_members as mb join activity_types as a on a.code = mb.activity_type where a.description = 'Research Organisations'

question: What are the country codes of institutions with the short name UTT, that are not in Switzerland?
query: select distinct countries.country_code2 from institutions join countries on institutions.country_id = countries.unics_id where institutions.short_name = 'UTT' and countries.country_name != 'Switzerland'

question: How many project members are businesses?
query: SELECT count(member_name) FROM project_members as t1 join activity_types as t2 on t1.activity_type = t2.code WHERE t2.code = 'PRC'

question: Retrieve the short names of institutions having a project member whose city is != "KINGSTON ON SOAR NOTTINGHAM" and acronym "ICEC"
query: select distinct institutions.short_name from project_members join institutions on project_members.institution_id = institutions.unics_id where institutions.acronym = 'ICEC' and project_members.city != 'KINGSTON ON SOAR NOTTINGHAM'

question: Show me the number of projects where Thomas Bell was principal investigator
query: select count(*) from projects as p join people as peep on p.principal_investigator = peep.unics_id where peep.full_name = 'Thomas Bell'

question: How many project members are Higher or Secondary Education Establishments?
query: SELECT count (distinct member_name) FROM project_members as t1 join activity_types as t2 on t1.activity_type = t2.code WHERE t2.code = 'HES'

question: What is the average cost of projects that didn't end in 2018-03-10 and are assigned to the department General Secretariat?
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from project_members join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where projects.end_date != '2018-03-10' and project_members.department_name = 'General Secretariat'

question: How many projects have been related to Robotics?
query: SELECT count(t3.title) from subject_areas as t1 join project_subject_areas as t2 on t1.code = t2.subject_area join projects as t3 on t2.project = t3.unics_id WHERE t1.title = 'Robotics'

question: What is the average cost of projects whose acronym is not PROX1, their members are located in BG and have territorial unit description Warszawski zachodni?
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from eu_territorial_units join project_members on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where eu_territorial_units.description = 'Warszawski zachodni' and project_members.country = 'BG' and projects.acronym != 'PROX1'

question: Find distinct titles of topics of projects that with end year 2014
query: SELECT distinct t.title FROM projects AS T1 join project_topics as pt on T1.unics_id = pt.project join topics as t on pt.topic = t.code where t1.end_year = 2014

question: Show me the short name of the institution with acronym INSERM which is a project member and has an eu territorial unit different from Lichtenfels?
query: select distinct institutions.short_name from project_members join institutions on project_members.institution_id = institutions.unics_id join eu_territorial_units on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 where institutions.acronym = 'INSERM' and eu_territorial_units.description != 'Lichtenfels'

question: What are the different panel descriptions associated with projects that didn't start in 2011?
query: select distinct erc_panels.description from project_erc_panels join erc_panels on project_erc_panels.panel = erc_panels.code join projects on projects.unics_id = project_erc_panels.project where projects.start_year != '2011'

question: How many non-EU entities have participated in projects?
query: SELECT count(distinct t1.member_name) FROM project_members as t1 join activity_types as t2 on t1.activity_type = t2.code join projects as p on t1.project = p.unics_id  WHERE t1.geocode_regions_3 = 'NONEU'

question: What is the total cost of the projects whose acronym is not COELUX and the panel description is Physical and Analytical Chemical sciences?
query: select sum(projects.total_cost) from project_erc_panels join projects on project_erc_panels.project = projects.unics_id join erc_panels on erc_panels.code = project_erc_panels.panel where erc_panels.description = 'Physical and Analytical Chemical sciences' and projects.acronym != 'COELUX'

question: What is the average cost of projects with title Modernisation of Vessels for Inland waterway freight Transport that are not assigned to the institution with acronym ICN2 and department Large Systems Business Unit?
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from institutions join project_members on institutions.unics_id = project_members.institution_id join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where institutions.acronym != 'ICN2' and projects.title = 'Modernisation of Vessels for Inland waterway freight Transport' and project_members.department_name = 'Large Systems Business Unit'

where: "Modernisation of Vessels for Inland waterway freight Transport"

query_toks: "Modernisation of Vessels for Inland waterway freight Transport"

question: Show the average total cost of projects that started in 2010 in which there is an institution involved with an acronym different than "CEA"

question: Compute the average total cost for projects whose relative ERC panel description equals to "Computer Science and Informatics" nad whose arconym equals "MARBIGEN"
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from erc_panels join project_erc_panels on erc_panels.code = project_erc_panels.panel join projects on project_erc_panels.project = projects.unics_id where erc_panels.description = 'Computer science and informatics' and projects.acronym = 'MARBIGEN'

question: display all panels that have a project whose start year is not 2010.
query: select erc_panels.description from projects join project_erc_panels on projects.unics_id = project_erc_panels.project join erc_panels on project_erc_panels.panel = erc_panels.code where projects.start_year != '2010'

question: What is the total cost of projects that ended before 2007 and don't have a programme with short name Reducing energy consumption and carbon footprint?
query: select sum(projects.total_cost) from programmes join project_programmes on programmes.code = project_programmes.programme join projects on project_programmes.project = projects.unics_id where programmes.short_name != 'Reducing energy consumption and carbon footprint' and projects.end_year < '2007'
values: Reducing energy consumption and carbon footprint

question: List all of the titles and the amount of funding that has been dispersed per programme
query: SELECT t1.title, sum(t3.ec_max_contribution) from programmes as t1 join project_programmes as t2 on t1.code = t2.programme join projects as t3 on t3.unics_id = t2.project group by t1.title

question: Compute the sum of total  costs for projects ending after 2019 and whose ERC panel description is "Evolutionary, population and environmental biology"
query: select sum(projects.total_cost) from erc_panels join project_erc_panels on erc_panels.code = project_erc_panels.panel join projects on project_erc_panels.project = projects.unics_id where erc_panels.description = 'Evolutionary, population and environmental biology' and projects.end_year > '2019'

question: Show me ERC panels for projects that end in or after 2022
query: select distinct erc_panels.description from projects join project_erc_panels on projects.unics_id = project_erc_panels.project join erc_panels on project_erc_panels.panel = erc_panels.code where projects.end_year >= '2022'

question: Find member name and role code of project members in project with acronym GTBB
query: select pm.member_name, pr.code from project_members as pm join projects as p on pm.project = p.unics_id join project_member_roles as pr on pm.member_role = pr.code where p.acronym = 'GTBB'

question: Which institutions have never been project coordinators
query: SELECT distinct member_name from project_members WHERE member_name NOT in (SELECT member_name from project_members where member_role = 'coordinator')

question: How many european research council panel descriptions are there for projects that do not have the acronym belenus?

question: Show the titles of all of the projects in the subject area of Climate change and Carbon cycle research

question: What is the average cost of projects assigned to CAMBRIDGE DESIGN PARTNERSHIP LLP institution, located in Wallis and Futuna with territorial unit description Северозападен?

question: How many project programmes are there, with projects that start in 2020 and members that are not from Cataluña?
query: select count(distinct programmes.title) from eu_territorial_units join project_members on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id join project_programmes on projects.unics_id = project_programmes.project join programmes on project_programmes.programme = programmes.code where eu_territorial_units.description != 'Cataluña' and projects.start_year = '2020'

question: Which funding scheme provided the most funding
query: SELECT t1.title, sum(ec_max_contribution) from funding_schemes as t1 join projects as t2 on t1.code = t2.ec_fund_scheme group by t1.title ORDER BY sum(ec_max_contribution) DESC LIMIT 1

question: What is the average cost of projects whose members are located in countries with code ID and have the territorial unit description Etelä-Karjala?
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from project_members join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id join eu_territorial_units on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join institutions on institutions.geocode_regions_3 = eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions join countries on countries.unics_id = institutions.country_id where countries.country_code2 = 'ID' and eu_territorial_units.description = 'Etelä-Karjala'

question: What is the title of the subject area that has been granted the least amount of funding
query: SELECT t1.title, MIN(t3.ec_max_contribution) from subject_areas as t1 join project_subject_areas as t2 on t1.code = t2.subject_area join projects as t3 on t2.project = t3.unics_id  group by t1.title order by  MIN(t3.ec_max_contribution) DESC LIMIT 1

question: Show the institution that has been involved in the highest number of projects
query: Select i.institutions_name, Count(distinct project) From project_members join institutions as i on project_members.institution_id = i.unics_id GROUP BY i.institutions_name order by count(distinct project) desc limit 1

question: What is the average cost of projects started in 2019, assigned to institutions located in Ivory Coast with eu territorial unit description Heinsberg?

question: Which institution has participated in the fewest projects

question: Show institutions from France except the ones from Paris

query: select count(distinct projects.end_date) from institutions join eu_territorial_units on institutions.geocode_regions_3 = eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions join countries on countries.unics_id = institutions.country_id join project_members on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where institutions.institutions_name != 'FONDAZIONE RI.MED' and countries.country_code2 = 'TH' and eu_territorial_units.description != 'Région lémanique'

question: What is the total cost of all DEMOBASE projects from all institutions except PSL?
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from institutions join eu_territorial_units on institutions.geocode_regions_3 = eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions join project_members on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where projects.acronym = 'DEMOBASE' and institutions.short_name != 'PSL'

question: What is the total cost of projects whose end year is after 2009 and are assigned to institutions in countries that don't have the country code GW?
query: select sum(projects.total_cost) from institutions join eu_territorial_units on institutions.geocode_regions_3 = eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions join countries on countries.unics_id = institutions.country_id join project_members on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where countries.country_code2 != 'GW' and projects.end_year > '2009'

question: What is the total cost of projects that are not in Western Sahara but in Riga and started before 2015-10-07
query: select count(distinct projects.total_cost) from countries join institutions on countries.unics_id = institutions.country_id join eu_territorial_units on institutions.geocode_regions_3 = eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions join project_members on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where countries.country_name != 'Western Sahara' and eu_territorial_units.description = 'Rīga' and projects.start_date <= '2015-10-07'

question: What is the average cost of projects assigned to institutions with the acronym EHESS, located in Somalia in the city DUNSTABLE?
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from institutions join eu_territorial_units on institutions.geocode_regions_3 = eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions join countries on countries.unics_id = institutions.country_id join project_members on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where countries.country_name = 'Somalia' and project_members.city = 'DUNSTABLE' and institutions.acronym != 'EHESS'

question: Show the acronym of projects with a member from Greece
query: Select p.acronym from projects as p join project_members as pm on p.unics_id = pm.project join institutions as i on pm.institution_id = i.unics_id join countries as c on i.country_id = c.unics_id where c.country_name = 'Greece'

question: What is the average total cost of projects that have members whose participating department is "Comune di Roma" and are not in the geocode region 3 of "Arr. Nivelles"?
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from project_members join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id join institutions on institutions.unics_id = project_members.institution_id join eu_territorial_units on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = institutions.geocode_regions_3 where project_members.department_name = 'Comune di Roma' and eu_territorial_units.description != 'Arr. Nivelles'

question: What is the average total cost of projects ending in 2015 or late, that have a member that is not from SESTO SAN GIOVANNI MILANO and an institution not from United States Virgin Islands?
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from countries join institutions on countries.unics_id = institutions.country_id join eu_territorial_units on institutions.geocode_regions_3 = eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions join project_members on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where countries.country_name != 'United States Virgin Islands' and projects.end_year >= '2015' and project_members.city != 'SESTO SAN GIOVANNI MILANO'

question: Show the name of members in projects costing less than the average project cost.
query: SELECT T1.member_name FROM project_members AS T1 JOIN projects AS T2 ON T1.project = T2.unics_id WHERE T2.total_cost < (SELECT AVG(T23.total_cost) FROM projects AS T23)

question: Find the code and title of the funding scheme which funded the highest number of projects.
query: select s.code, s.title from funding_schemes as s where s.code = (select s2.code from funding_schemes as s2 join projects as p on s2.code = p.ec_fund_scheme group by s2.code order by count(*) desc LIMIT 1)

question: What is the average cost of projects from Fundació Pau Costa in TV and LU
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from countries join institutions on countries.unics_id = institutions.country_id join eu_territorial_units on institutions.geocode_regions_3 = eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions join project_members on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where institutions.short_name = 'Fundació Pau Costa' and countries.country_code2 = 'TV' and project_members.country = 'LU'

question: What is the average total cost of all projects that end in 2013 or earlier and a have a member institution whose acronym is UCBL?
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from institutions join eu_territorial_units on institutions.geocode_regions_3 = eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions join project_members on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where institutions.acronym = 'UCBL' and projects.end_year <= '2013'

question: What is the title of the subject area that has been granted the most funding
query: SELECT t1.title, MAX(t3.ec_max_contribution) from subject_areas as t1 join project_subject_areas as t2 on t1.code = t2.subject_area join projects as t3 on t2.project = t3.unics_id  group by t1.title order by  MAX(t3.ec_max_contribution) DESC LIMIT 1

question: Show the total cost of projects with a starting date equal or greater than 2019-10-30 and where at least one participant is from South Georgia
query: select sum(projects.total_cost) from project_members join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id join institutions on institutions.unics_id = project_members.institution_id join countries on countries.unics_id = institutions.country_id where projects.start_date >= '2019-10-30' and countries.country_name = 'South Georgia'

question: Show the amount of funding and corresponding list of industrial partners that have worked on projects in order from the most funding to the least funding
query: SELECT t1.member_name, p.ec_max_contribution FROM project_members as t1 join activity_types as t2 on t1.activity_type = t2.code join projects as p on t1.project = p.unics_id WHERE t2.code = 'PRC' ORDER BY ec_max_contribution DESC

question: Show all names of institutions from France except institutions from the territorial region of Paris
query: select i.institutions_name from institutions as i join countries as c on c.unics_id = i.country_id where country_name = 'France' except select i.institutions_name from institutions as i join countries as c on c.unics_id = i.country_id join eu_territorial_units as etu on i.geocode_regions_3 = etu.geocode_regions where country_name = 'France' and etu.description = 'Paris'

question: Which non-EU entity has recieved the most funding through a project?
query: SELECT t1.member_name, p.ec_max_contribution FROM project_members as t1 join activity_types as t2 on t1.activity_type = t2.code join projects as p on t1.project = p.unics_id WHERE t1.geocode_regions_3 = 'NONEU' ORDER BY ec_max_contribution DESC LIMIT 1

question: Show me the average project costs of projects having an institution as project member where the institution acronym is “CED” and the institution’s country name “Wallis and Futuna”
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from eu_territorial_units join project_members on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join institutions on institutions.geocode_regions_3 = eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions join countries on countries.unics_id = institutions.country_id join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where countries.country_name = 'Wallis and Futuna' and institutions.acronym = 'CED'

question: Show the total cost of projects that end on "2017-07-13" and have a participant located in "Wilhelmshaven, Kreisfreie Stadt"
query: select sum(projects.total_cost) from institutions join project_members on institutions.unics_id = project_members.institution_id join eu_territorial_units on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = institutions.geocode_regions_3 join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where eu_territorial_units.description = 'Wilhelmshaven, Kreisfreie Stadt' and projects.end_date = '2017-07-13'

question: What is the average total cost of projects of members that are not from Outer London East and North East and do not have the acronym Antepigenetics
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from eu_territorial_units join institutions on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = institutions.geocode_regions_3 join project_members on institutions.unics_id = project_members.institution_id join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where eu_territorial_units.description != 'Outer London – East and North East' and projects.acronym != 'ANTEPIGENETICS'
values: Outer London – East and North East

question: What is the total cost of the projects whose members are in the country LY and their institution location is the country of Republic of the Congo?
query: select sum(projects.total_cost) from eu_territorial_units join project_members on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id join institutions on institutions.geocode_regions_3 = eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions join countries on countries.unics_id = institutions.country_id where countries.country_name = 'Republic of the Congo' and project_members.country = 'LY'

question: Show the institution that has been involved in the least amount of projects
query: Select t2.institutions_name, Count(distinct project) From project_members as t1 join institutions as t2 on t1.institution_id = t2.unics_id GROUP BY t2.institutions_name order by count(distinct project) asc limit 1

question: Show the industrial partners that have worked on projects and the amount of funding they have recieved in order from most to least
query: SELECT t1.member_name, p.ec_max_contribution FROM project_members as t1 join activity_types as t2 on t1.activity_type = t2.code join projects as p on t1.project = p.unics_id WHERE t2.code = 'PRC' ORDER BY ec_max_contribution DESC

question: Added total cost of projects with a member from a Medical Engineering department outside the region of Hildburghausen.
query: select sum(projects.total_cost) from eu_territorial_units join institutions on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = institutions.geocode_regions_3 join project_members on institutions.unics_id = project_members.institution_id join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where eu_territorial_units.description != 'Hildburghausen' and project_members.department_name = 'Medical Engineering'

question: Which funding scheme provided the least funding
query: SELECT t1.title, sum(ec_max_contribution) from funding_schemes as t1 join projects as t2 on t1.code = t2.ec_fund_scheme group by t1.title ORDER BY sum(ec_max_contribution) ASC LIMIT 1

question: What is the total cost of all projects that do not have the country code TT with members from Newtec Belgium but are not from Ловеч
query: select sum(projects.total_cost) from project_members join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id join eu_territorial_units on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join institutions on institutions.geocode_regions_3 = eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions join countries on countries.unics_id = institutions.country_id where countries.country_code2 != 'TT' and project_members.member_short_name != 'Newtec Belgium' and eu_territorial_units.description != 'Ловеч'

question: Which non-EU entity has recieved the least funding through a project?
query: SELECT t1.member_name, p.ec_max_contribution FROM project_members as t1 join activity_types as t2 on t1.activity_type = t2.code join projects as p on t1.project = p.unics_id WHERE t1.geocode_regions_3 = 'NONEU' ORDER BY ec_max_contribution ASC LIMIT 1

question: What is the total cost of projects assigned to the institution with short name UTBM for all the departments except Civiele bescherming?
query: select sum(projects.total_cost) from eu_territorial_units join project_members on eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions = project_members.geocode_regions_3 join institutions on institutions.geocode_regions_3 = eu_territorial_units.geocode_regions join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where project_members.department_name != 'Civiele bescherming' and institutions.short_name = 'UTBM'

question: What is the average cost of projects assigned to the institute with acronym EURECAT located in Mauritius?
query: select avg(projects.total_cost) from countries join institutions on countries.unics_id = institutions.country_id join project_members on institutions.unics_id = project_members.institution_id join projects on project_members.project = projects.unics_id where countries.country_name = 'Mauritius' and institutions.acronym = 'EURECAT'
